CURSOR TASK — TV SHOW EPISODES VIEW (SEASONS + EPISODES)
=====================================================================

ROLE
You are a senior product designer + senior frontend + senior backend engineer.

Goal: add a breath-taking premium TV episodes experience with season toggling,
episode progress tracking, and clean interaction for desktop and TV on top where it says cast

---------------------------------------------------------------------
REQUIRED FEATURES
---------------------------------------------------------------------
• Episodes tab on TV show details page
• Season selector (switch seasons)
• Episode list per season
• Resume logic (episode-aware)
• Episode progress tracking per profile
• Works on desktop and Android TV

---------------------------------------------------------------------
BACKEND REQUIREMENTS
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Implement:
GET /v1/shows/:showId/seasons
GET /v1/shows/:showId/seasons/:seasonNumber/episodes?profileId=...

Ensure:
• Episodes sorted by episode_number asc
• Progress merged into episode response
• Fast response (indexed by show_id + season_number)

---------------------------------------------------------------------
FRONTEND REQUIREMENTS
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Episodes Tab:
• Default to last watched season OR season 1
• Season selector changes episodes without route change
• Smooth transition between seasons (loading skeleton allowed)
• Episode cards show:
  - episode number
  - title
  - runtime
  - progress bar (if started)
  - watched indicator (if completed)

Play Behavior:
• “Play” resumes last watched episode
• Auto-advance to next episode if completed
• Auto-advance season if last episode completed

---------------------------------------------------------------------
ANDROID TV RULES
---------------------------------------------------------------------
• All items must be focusable
• Season selector must be navigable via D-pad
• Episode list must preserve focus on season change
• Focus ring must be visible and consistent

---------------------------------------------------------------------
DATA RULES
---------------------------------------------------------------------
• Episode progress is per profile
• Episode completion ≥ 90%
• Hide progress bar if < 2%

---------------------------------------------------------------------
FINAL EXIT GATE
---------------------------------------------------------------------
[ ] Seasons load correctly
[ ] Switching seasons works without navigation
[ ] Episodes display cleanly
[ ] Progress tracking is accurate
[ ] Resume logic works end-to-end
[ ] Android TV navigation works
[ ] No placeholder or fake logic

